---------------------------------------
PPopupMenu
---------------------------------------
You can easily create PopupMenu and add items to menu in Processing code.

---------------------------------------
Working Environment
---------------------------------------
Any environment that Processing works
-Mac(OSX)
-Windows
-Linux

---------------------------------------
Installation
---------------------------------------
Download the file ppopupmenu and extract it to <processing-sketches>/libraries/.
Renamed hixi-hyi-ppopupmenu-*** to ppopupmenu.
Mac[ex]:  /Users/<Username>/Documents/Processing/libraries/ppopupmenu

---------------------------------------
How to set up new code
---------------------------------------
1.Launch Processing and create a new code.
2.Select "Sketch -> import Library... -> ppopupmenu".
3.Now, you can use "PPopupMenu" in this code.

---------------------------------------
Examples
---------------------------------------
1.Select "File -> Example...".
2.Show "Contributed Libraries -> ppopupmenu".
3.Now, you can see sample code.

